obo:GO_0003674  a  owl:Class .

gomodel:SYNGO_762  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: The paper characterizes the GAT1 knockout mice.\nFigure 1D demonstrates a loss of 3h-GABA uptake in hippocampal syanptosomes from the deficient mice.. Experimental description: 'The mRNA was synthesized in vitro from each of these clones and was tested for its ability to express functional GABA transporters in Xenopus oocytes.'\n'The purification of a rat brain GABA transporter protein (4) provided a\nreagent for the molecular cloning of a GABA transporter cDNA.'" ;
